thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Michael

author: Michael
title: Michael
text:
Am Frame sells good products. The website is a bit heavy-handed, preferring you to buy everything needed to frame a print, e.g., mat boards, backing, and glass/acrylic. If you are interested in one piece of the puzzle, the site can be a bit frustrating.
The frame selection is a bit minimal, but the quality of the goods is very good.
Phone and customer service is good and reliable.
